### Advancia PayLedger API Tests
### Admin & Support Operations

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@adminToken = your-admin-jwt-token-here

### Get All Users (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get System Analytics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/analytics
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get System Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/system/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Create Support Ticket
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/support/tickets
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Support Ticket",
  "description": "This is a test support ticket for API testing",
  "category": "TECHNICAL",
  "priority": "MEDIUM"
}

###

### Get Support Tickets
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/support/tickets
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Update Support Ticket Status
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/support/tickets/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}

###

### Add Comment to Support Ticket
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/support/tickets/1/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "This is a test comment on the support ticket"
}

###

### Get Audit Logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/audit-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get Notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Mark Notification as Read
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/1/read
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Send Push Notification (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/notifications/push
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Notification",
  "body": "This is a test push notification",
  "userId": 1
}

###

### Get User Statistics (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/stats/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get Transaction Statistics (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/stats/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json